34:27.332 --> 34:28.899
Hi.

34:30.502 --> 34:33.036
Hey, can I ask you a question?

34:34.306 --> 34:36.173
I'm new here
to the neighborhood, and...

34:36.175 --> 34:39.409
It's Brian, right?
Phone for you.

34:48.287 --> 34:49.886
Yeah. This is Brian.

34:49.888 --> 34:53.690
Pack it in, sparkle pants.
You're off the Novo case.

34:53.692 --> 34:55.158
Give me a second.

34:55.160 --> 34:56.359
I'm getting somewhere here.

34:56.361 --> 34:59.129
<i> -There is no there there.</i>
-English.

34:59.131 --> 35:03.033
You're off the Novo case
because there is no Novo case.

35:03.035 --> 35:03.733
So they got the guy?

35:03.735 --> 35:08.004
<i> There is no guy, and there</i>
<i> never will be a guy.</i>

35:08.006 --> 35:09.372
It's almost finished.

35:09.374 --> 35:12.275
The movie that Novo was doing
with his fiancee?

35:12.277 --> 35:14.878
Eight million dollars worth
of two-fisted western

35:14.880 --> 35:16.680
coming to a theater
near you at Easter.

35:16.682 --> 35:18.081
<i> So the studio</i>
<i> called the mayor,</i>

35:18.083 --> 35:19.616
<i> the mayor called</i>
<i> the commissioner,</i>

35:19.618 --> 35:20.650
<i> the commissioner</i>
<i> called our boss</i>

35:20.652 --> 35:23.553
and told him what we all
should have known
from the jump.

35:23.555 --> 35:25.922
When a studio's
got $8 million invested,

35:25.924 --> 35:29.960
stars can be dead,
but they can't be dead homos.

35:31.396 --> 35:33.697
So that's it. I'm just done?

35:33.966 --> 35:36.600
Tip your barman
on the way out.

35:52.050 --> 35:53.517
(SIGHS)

35:53.719 --> 35:54.384
Sorry, I just...

35:54.386 --> 35:56.253
-That's okay.
-Just give me a few minutes,

35:56.255 --> 35:57.254
-and I'll...
-Baby, baby...

35:57.256 --> 35:59.156
-...try it again.
-That's okay.

35:59.158 --> 35:59.789
No, it's not all right.

35:59.791 --> 36:02.959
-Just let me do it again.
-Eddie. Eddie.

36:02.961 --> 36:04.528
Can I tell you something
without you getting mad?

36:04.530 --> 36:08.198
You're not the first guy
that I've been with
that this has happened to.

36:08.200 --> 36:10.100
We're not
in high school anymore.

36:10.102 --> 36:12.135
I wish to hell I was.

36:12.337 --> 36:15.505
Come on. Let's give it a rest.

36:38.830 --> 36:40.397
Hey, Paul Lynde.

36:40.399 --> 36:42.165
Thanks for your help.

36:43.936 --> 36:44.367
What help?

36:44.369 --> 36:48.705
You had to know when I
walked in that bar
I was gonna get shut down.

36:48.707 --> 36:52.909
Well, I thought we might be
faster than
the Hollywood machine.

36:52.911 --> 36:54.711
Long shot.

36:55.647 --> 36:59.516
You're somewhat exercised
for a guy who thought
he'd catch a limp wrist

36:59.518 --> 37:00.217
just by drinking their beer.

37:00.219 --> 37:04.387
I like catching killers.
Don't need to think too much
on the details.

37:04.389 --> 37:04.955
Mighty big of you.

37:04.957 --> 37:08.625
Why the hell
are you so up with people
on a bunch of homos anyway?

37:08.627 --> 37:09.993
No, really, I... I get it.

37:09.995 --> 37:11.494
Some otherwise
nice-seeming guys,

37:11.496 --> 37:13.563
sad to see them
wreck their lives like that,

37:13.565 --> 37:16.266
but it's still deviant, huh?

37:16.268 --> 37:17.968
Still...

37:18.737 --> 37:19.803
Wrong.

37:19.805 --> 37:24.708
Well, I thought you were
of the "free your mind,
roll your own" generation.

37:24.710 --> 37:25.408
Don't act dumb, all right?

37:25.410 --> 37:28.211
There is a line,
and they stick their necks
out crossing it.

37:28.213 --> 37:31.014
And they know it.
You know what it is?

37:31.016 --> 37:33.216
They're... They're addicted.

37:33.218 --> 37:34.884
Yeah, like all
the junkies I see.

37:34.886 --> 37:38.922
And they know something
can go wrong,
and they do it anyway.

37:39.491 --> 37:41.391
They're just sick.

37:41.927 --> 37:42.859
It's sad.

37:42.861 --> 37:46.663
And for what, huh?
How the hell is it worth
the risk to do that?

37:46.665 --> 37:49.933
You know what I realized
trying to understand people?

37:49.935 --> 37:52.736
-What?
-Don't try to understand 'em.

37:53.639 --> 37:56.773
I know what I'd kill for
and what I'd die for.

37:56.775 --> 37:57.407
You served. You do, too.

37:57.409 --> 38:00.744
And every day on this job,
we get to see what other
people would kill and die for

38:00.746 --> 38:03.246
and I used to think
it was different,
but it's not.

38:03.248 --> 38:07.050
It's the same. Love, hate.

38:07.052 --> 38:09.252
With a side of stupid.

38:11.757 --> 38:13.657
You seem...

38:14.326 --> 38:15.692
Old?

38:17.763 --> 38:19.396
You okay?

38:20.399 --> 38:21.831
Well...

38:22.034 --> 38:25.001
(SIGHS)
Go home and kiss your wife.

38:29.007 --> 38:30.907
You can count on that.

38:58.270 --> 39:01.338
(INAUDIBLE)

39:18.657 --> 39:21.624
Hiya, Ed.
Thought you punched out.

39:21.760 --> 39:23.593
Yeah, I did.

39:26.365 --> 39:28.765
Hey, uh, you got the time?

39:28.767 --> 39:30.433
Yeah, sure.

39:57.496 --> 40:00.797
SADIE: Charlie? We're back.

40:10.242 --> 40:12.108
Mother Mary.

40:13.345 --> 40:15.945
Look at that blessing.

40:17.416 --> 40:19.682
You see it in her eyes.

40:20.752 --> 40:23.319
The wounded little bird.

40:23.989 --> 40:25.722
Mother...

40:26.391 --> 40:27.824
Lover...

40:27.926 --> 40:29.659
(WHISPERS)
Goddess.

40:29.661 --> 40:32.162
Let me back into your heart.

40:32.998 --> 40:36.633
-Charlie, I...
-I know, I know, I...

40:36.635 --> 40:39.335
-I hurt you.
-You didn't hurt me, Charlie.

40:39.337 --> 40:41.838
You... Hurt me.

40:41.840 --> 40:43.406
I saw stars.

40:43.408 --> 40:46.509
I couldn't chew for a week.

40:46.511 --> 40:49.145
I won't apologize for passion.

40:49.681 --> 40:51.347
I love you.

40:52.417 --> 40:54.651
I love you so much.

40:55.487 --> 40:56.886
Mary...

40:57.189 --> 41:00.690
Mary, you are the light,

41:00.826 --> 41:04.060
and I am
the lighthouse keeper.

41:04.362 --> 41:07.030
-(BEADS CLATTERING)
-KATIE: Mary?

41:08.366 --> 41:11.100
Oh, my God!

41:17.142 --> 41:18.942
Is it yours?

41:19.277 --> 41:21.010
I don't know.

41:22.080 --> 41:24.447
Is it mine, cherry pie?

41:34.926 --> 41:36.526
It's ours.

41:37.696 --> 41:39.095
Yes.

41:41.466 --> 41:43.833
And we'll raise it together.

41:43.902 --> 41:46.402
We are a revolution.

41:47.305 --> 41:49.372
And one day,

41:49.641 --> 41:52.242
the world will know our name.

41:52.978 --> 41:54.511
KATIE: Yes.
